content.body:
### Shop 205/70R16 Tire Size The 205/70R16 tire size is one you’ll find on crossovers like the Buick Encore, Jeep Liberty, Jeep Patriot and Suzuki Sidekick. For most drivers, all-season tires are a great choice thanks to their combination of year round traction even in light snow, good road manners, predictable handling and a quiet ride on the highway. For some great premium 205/70R16 all-season tires, check out the Continental ContiProContact, [Firestone Destination LE3](https://simpletire.com/brands/firestone-tires/destination-le3), or Falken Ziex CT60 A/S. Popular makes and models: Buick Encore (2013-2021)
Jeep Liberty (2007-2014)
Jeep Patriot (2007-2017)
Suzuki Sidekick (1989-1998) Most drivers want a set of tires that are built to last, so tires with a long tread life warranty become a must. Consider the Hankook Kinergy PT (H737), General Altimax RT43, [Yokohama Avid Ascend LX](https://simpletire.com/brands/yokohama-tires/avid-ascend-lx), and Nexen N Priz AH8 if you’re looking for a set of 205/70R16 tires that are expected to last over 65,000 miles. All-season tires are great for dry, wet, and light winter weather, but they tend to struggle in moderate to severe winter weather conditions. Fortunately, winter tires are built to conquer the worst that winter can throw at them, so take a look at the Yokohama iceGUARD G075, Toyo Observe GSI-5, Dunlop Grandtrek SJ6, and [GT Radial IcePro 3](https://simpletire.com/brands/gt-radial-tires/icepro-3) to give your ride extra traction in ice, slush, and snow. Whether you drive a Buick Encore, Jeep Patriot, Suzuki Sidekick, or something else, SimpleTire has a set of 205/70R16 tires that meets your needs at a great price!
